Vi commands (pronounced 'vee eye')

vi test.txt

after opening to write some text you have to enter in 'insert mode'

you can do that pressing the 'i' key

try typing some words

then press the 'ESC' key to exit 'Insert mode'

now to save the text type

:w

and press enter

to quit:

:q

done!

remember to press the 'i' key to enable 'insert mode' or you will do a mess
